30
00:02:50,565 --> 00:02:52,965
<i>Yeah, well, I should talk.</i>

31
00:02:53,098 --> 00:02:55,832
<i>I didn't know back then</i>
<i>how bad it was gonna get,</i>

32
00:02:55,965 --> 00:02:58,532
<i>and it got real bad.</i>

33
00:03:01,132 --> 00:03:03,598
[Kasane]
You shouldn't pursue him
in your condition.

34
00:03:03,732 --> 00:03:07,432
I know what I am doing.
This necessity.

35
00:03:07,565 --> 00:03:09,532
There is no stopping me.

36
00:03:09,665 --> 00:03:11,665
Ah, that's far enough, ladies.

37
00:03:11,798 --> 00:03:16,498
Sorry, but Izaya
told me to make sure
not to let anyone get by.

38
00:03:16,632 --> 00:03:20,532
