if you're not
a hundred percent.

41
00:03:24,665 --> 00:03:26,132
But, if you really wanna,

42
00:03:26,265 --> 00:03:30,198
I won't mind it.
I'd be happy to oblige.

43
00:03:30,332 --> 00:03:31,698
Not that it'll matter much.

44
00:03:31,832 --> 00:03:33,232
I can't think
of anything lamer

45
00:03:33,365 --> 00:03:34,998
than those guys
fighting to the death.

46
00:03:35,132 --> 00:03:37,098
Oh, well! If that's
how it's gotta be,

47
00:03:37,232 --> 00:03:39,232
