[groans]
Huh?

52
00:03:54,565 --> 00:03:57,132
[laughing]

53
00:03:57,265 --> 00:03:59,732
Aw, poor Seitaro!

54
00:03:59,865 --> 00:04:01,365
Shizuo's incredible,
isn't he?

55
00:04:01,498 --> 00:04:03,332
I was hiding back there
and saw everything.

56
00:04:03,465 --> 00:04:05,932
And did you see how
he blocked that excavator?

57
00:04:06,065 --> 00:04:08,632
That was so amazing,
I almost peed my pants!

58
00:04:08,765 --> 00:04:10,132
What the hell
are you doing here?

59
00:04:10,265 --> 00:04:12,698
I heard Ms. Kasane
kidnapped my son,

60
00:04:12,832 --> 00:04:14,832
so, naturally,
I figured you were behind it,

61
00:04:14,965 --> 00:04:17,632
and... I was right.

62
00:04:17,765 --> 00:04:21,565
Your son?
What are you talking about?

63
00:04:21,698 --> 00:04:24,265
[gasps]
There she is!

64
00:04:24,398 --> 00:04:26,232
God, she's still beautiful!

65
