147
00:08:42,105 --> 00:08:43,138
What a day.

148
00:08:43,271 --> 00:08:44,738
Sorry about Varona.

149
00:08:44,871 --> 00:08:46,638
I'll make sure
and have a talk with her.

150
00:08:46,771 --> 00:08:48,271
Nah, it's cool.

151
00:08:48,405 --> 00:08:51,205
She works for us now,
so I'll deal with it.

152
00:08:51,338 --> 00:08:52,905
Bet I know what's with her.

153
00:08:53,038 --> 00:08:54,471
She's probably
still messed up

154
00:08:54,605 --> 00:08:57,338
over Shizuo gettin'
pinched by the cops.

155
00:08:57,471 --> 00:08:59,238
[thinking]
<i>If I only knew what</i>
<i>was really goin' on</i>

156
00:08:59,371 --> 00:09:01,038
<i>between her and Shizuo...</i>

157
00:09:01,171 --> 00:09:03,471
<i>Nah. They'd still be</i>
<i>where they are</i>

158
00:09:03,605 --> 00:09:06,705
<i>and I'd still be here,</i>
<i>eating sushi.</i>

159
00:09:06,838 --> 00:09:08,138
<i>I'd be alone, either way.</i>

160
00:09:08,271 --> 00:09:11,805
Hey, Shizuo good person.
Is being enzai.

