like more engawa?

164
00:09:19,538 --> 00:09:22,438
Buy now, pay with
Japanese En-- uh, Yen!

165
00:09:22,571 --> 00:09:24,238
I swear, Simon!

166
00:09:24,371 --> 00:09:27,238
I think you know more Japanese
than you're lettin' on.

167
00:09:27,371 --> 00:09:29,338
What's wrong, Simon?

168
00:09:31,171 --> 00:09:33,538
