169
00:09:36,371 --> 00:09:39,838
[gasps]
[overlapping voices]
<i>I love you.</i>

170
00:09:39,971 --> 00:09:42,438
Wh-- What the hell's
goin' on out here?

171
00:09:42,571 --> 00:09:45,438
[overlapping voices]
<i>I love you.</i>

172
00:09:45,571 --> 00:09:48,438
