or somethin'?

173
00:09:48,571 --> 00:09:53,305
[overlapping voices]
<i>I love you.</i>

174
00:09:53,438 --> 00:09:54,338
[gasps]

175
00:09:54,471 --> 00:09:55,838
Hey, mister.

176
00:09:55,971 --> 00:09:57,605
