comes around.

186
00:10:28,671 --> 00:10:30,205
What's with everyone?

187
00:10:30,338 --> 00:10:32,538
They're all acting
like how Amphisbaena did!

188
00:10:32,671 --> 00:10:35,305
Don't worry, I told them
not to infect you.

189
00:10:35,438 --> 00:10:37,438
Not for now anyway.

190
00:10:37,571 --> 00:10:39,005
Uh, oh, good.

191
00:10:39,138 --> 00:10:42,171
I never dreamed I could
have so many this fast.

192
00:10:42,305 --> 00:10:45,138
Who knew fingernails
and teeth could be Saika, too?

193
00:10:45,271 --> 00:10:47,338
I'm glad I took the time
to experiment.

194
00:10:47,471 --> 00:10:50,105
Without your help,
I wouldn't have

195
00:10:50,238 --> 00:10:51,871
this kind of power
at my fingertips.

196
00:10:52,005 --> 00:10:55,105
I'm grateful, Haruna.
Yes.

197
00:10:55,238 --> 00:10:58,771
Well, by tomorrow--
oh, correction-- today.

198
00:10:58,905 --> 00:11:02,538
By the end of today,
we'll settle all the scores.
Yes.

199
00:11:02,671 --> 00:11:05,771
Once we're done,
I'm going to treat you so good.

200
00:11:05,905 --> 00:11:09,571
I hope you're looking
forward to it, Haruna.

201
00:11:09,705 --> 00:11:12,371
Yes, Mother.

202
00:11:12,505 --> 00:11:15,171
[thinking]
<i>Why don't I feel</i>
<i>the same rush I did?</i>

203
00:11:15,305 --> 00:11:17,205
<i>Why am I not more excited?</i>

204
00:11:17,338 --> 00:11:19,205
[Tom] <i>Something was</i>
<i>definitely goin' on,</i>

205
00:11:19,338 --> 00:11:22,338
